<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="very-adj">very <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'veri/    美 /'veri/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-actual">1.★ <strong>正是的；恰好的 (actual)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He might be phoning her <strong>at this very moment</strong>.
他这会儿也许正在给她打电话呢。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That’s <strong>the very thing</strong> that I need.
那正是我需要的东西。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>仅仅的；唯独的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The <strong>very thought of</strong> speaking before many people frightens me.
一想到要在许多人面前讲话，我就发怵。</p></div></div>